1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,229
Characters, actions, places, occupations, and events in this series are fictional and created for entertainment purposes only.

2
00:00:07,229 --> 00:00:10,911
They are not intended to urge or promote any behavior in the series.

3
00:00:10,911 --> 00:00:13,076
Viewer discretion is advised.

4
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:15,313
You keep mentioning your grandma.

5
00:00:15,313 --> 00:00:16,613
Your granted wish is about her, right?

6
00:00:16,613 --> 00:00:17,968
My wish was to find her.

7
00:00:17,968 --> 00:00:19,352
That’s why 
you don’t want to get involved in a fight.

8
00:00:19,352 --> 00:00:20,908
So you made these pants to intimidate others.

9
00:00:20,908 --> 00:00:23,766
Although the pants are fake, 
they are important to me.

10
00:00:23,766 --> 00:00:26,062
When will you handle Oh?

11
00:00:26,062 --> 00:00:26,690
Where is it?

12
00:00:26,690 --> 00:00:28,482
The badge that you said you were taking back.

13
00:00:28,482 --> 00:00:31,044
If I take it back, will you stop?

14
00:00:31,044 --> 00:00:33,068
You know how much the pants mean to me.

15
00:00:33,068 --> 00:00:34,298
But you took them anyway.

16
00:00:34,298 --> 00:00:35,026
Take it.

17
00:00:35,369 --> 00:00:36,942
And stay away from me.

18
00:00:37,132 --> 00:00:38,179
I like you.

19
00:00:52,816 --> 00:00:53,352
Huh?

20
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:56,309
I like you.

21
00:01:03,047 --> 00:01:04,048
Are you out of your mind?

22
00:01:05,078 --> 00:01:06,717
Do you remember what you did to me?

23
00:01:07,079 --> 00:01:09,155
It’s unbelievable that 
you still have the nerve to tell me this.

24
00:01:09,155 --> 00:01:10,187
I really like you.

25
00:01:11,026 --> 00:01:12,863
I know you feel the same way.

26
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:14,529
You don’t know anything, Tum.

27
00:01:14,880 --> 00:01:16,001
Why not?

28
00:01:17,565 --> 00:01:19,609
You’re the one 
who is afraid to admit your feelings.

29
00:01:22,088 --> 00:01:22,670
Okay.

30
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,000
Fine.

31
00:01:24,553 --> 00:01:25,932
You said I’m afraid.

32
00:01:27,362 --> 00:01:28,384
And you think you’ve got the guts?

33
00:01:30,959 --> 00:01:32,667
I’m confessing my feelings for you.

34
00:01:33,220 --> 00:01:34,939
I admit it, Oh.

35
00:01:35,454 --> 00:01:36,771
You like me, so what?

36
00:01:37,248 --> 00:01:38,411
Do you have the guts to tell everyone?

37
00:01:47,849 --> 00:01:48,501
My friends…

38
00:01:48,501 --> 00:01:51,857
Are you doing this 
so you can mistreat me in front of others

39
00:01:52,010 --> 00:01:53,578
and make it up to me later?

40
00:01:53,673 --> 00:01:54,932
And you expect me to understand you?

41
00:01:55,867 --> 00:01:56,606
Is this what you want?

42
00:01:58,570 --> 00:01:59,440
Oh, that’s not what I…

43
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:00,507
Do I need to be understanding of you?

44
00:02:02,281 --> 00:02:03,047
Answer me.

45
00:02:08,274 --> 00:02:10,774
You are the one who refuses to take ownership.

46
00:02:16,068 --> 00:02:17,431
Oh, wait.

47
00:02:17,793 --> 00:02:18,592
Oh.

48
00:03:28,390 --> 00:03:30,494
I saw with my own eyes

49
00:03:30,685 --> 00:03:32,997
that Tum knocked Oh out in one punch.

50
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:38,477
I heard that he has a tattoo of Nuea-in badge 
on his chest.

51
00:03:38,954 --> 00:03:41,205
He is the best leader in our gang’s history.

52
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:47,473
Pathumphaisan students are too afraid 
to ambush us at the bridge.

53
00:03:48,331 --> 00:03:51,440
I heard that Oh is so embarrassed

54
00:03:51,650 --> 00:03:53,381
that he doesn’t come to school.

55
00:03:53,381 --> 00:03:55,353
Tum is the real deal.

56
00:04:20,737 --> 00:04:21,616
CHINESE SHRINES.

57
00:04:22,379 --> 00:04:24,193
Your granted wish is about your grandma, right?

58
00:04:24,193 --> 00:04:25,534
My wish was to find her.

59
00:04:25,534 --> 00:04:26,886
Did you find her?

60
00:04:26,886 --> 00:04:27,467
Yes.

61
00:04:28,059 --> 00:04:29,277
We found her at a Chinese shrine 
in my neighborhood.

62
00:04:35,781 --> 00:04:36,853
Where is your house?

63
00:04:37,330 --> 00:04:38,319
It’s close to my school.

64
00:04:43,647 --> 00:04:45,591
CHINESE SHRINES NEAR ME.

65
00:04:48,377 --> 00:04:51,414
CHAO PHO JUI SHRINE, 
BANG BUA THONG.

66
00:05:01,267 --> 00:05:04,369
PATHUMPHAISAN TECHNICAL INSTITUTE

67
00:05:04,846 --> 00:05:05,981
How long have they been here?

68
00:05:06,839 --> 00:05:07,567
A while.

69
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,201
2 vs. 8.

70
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:40,293
CHAO PHO JUI SHRINE, 
BANG BUA THONG
(You arrived at the destination.)

71
00:05:56,719 --> 00:05:58,067
Why did you come to this shrine?

72
00:06:01,826 --> 00:06:02,520
Nothing.

73
00:06:03,588 --> 00:06:04,298
It’s nothing.

74
00:06:18,548 --> 00:06:19,720
Are you done, Grandma?

75
00:06:20,578 --> 00:06:22,569
You have been praying for three hours.

76
00:06:25,583 --> 00:06:27,754
You should let the gods take some rest.

77
00:06:29,261 --> 00:06:31,583
What are you saying, Oh?

78
00:06:31,945 --> 00:06:33,680
I just got here.

79
00:06:34,634 --> 00:06:35,921
No, you didn’t.

80
00:06:36,646 --> 00:06:38,179
I’ll let you pray one last time.

81
00:06:38,599 --> 00:06:40,834
Then I’ll call an emergency service 
to capture you.

82
00:06:42,036 --> 00:06:43,184
That’s too much.

83
00:06:43,489 --> 00:06:45,889
I’m a human, not a snake.

84
00:06:46,728 --> 00:06:48,056
Come on, Grandma.

85
00:07:19,797 --> 00:07:21,047
Did you come here to see Oh?

86
00:07:49,773 --> 00:07:53,196
Tum, what’s going on between you and Oh?

87
00:07:57,163 --> 00:07:57,947
It’s nothing.

88
00:08:04,143 --> 00:08:07,307
You risked getting beaten and 
went to his school to search for the shrine.

89
00:08:08,451 --> 00:08:09,881
Stop lying.

90
00:08:10,682 --> 00:08:11,437
To be honest,

91
00:08:12,352 --> 00:08:13,458
I already knew about you two.

92
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:15,763
You knew?

93
00:08:16,278 --> 00:08:16,790
Yes.

94
00:08:17,076 --> 00:08:18,365
I went to see you at the temple.

95
00:08:18,365 --> 00:08:18,989
What?

96
00:08:25,131 --> 00:08:25,891
Do you want it?

97
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:26,947
Take it.

98
00:08:26,947 --> 00:08:28,603
You can’t take it back.

99
00:08:42,278 --> 00:08:43,558
(I wasn’t even secretly watching.)

100
00:08:43,939 --> 00:08:46,096
(You seemed to be in a world 
where there were only you two.)

101
00:08:47,508 --> 00:08:48,445
Let’s compete.

102
00:08:48,636 --> 00:08:49,136
Sure.

103
00:08:49,479 --> 00:08:50,365
Do you see me?

104
00:09:04,715 --> 00:09:05,822
Are you mad at me?

105
00:09:08,797 --> 00:09:10,149
Why would I be mad at you?

106
00:09:12,934 --> 00:09:13,890
For me,

107
00:09:14,767 --> 00:09:16,486
friends are more important 
than our school’s reputation.

108
00:09:23,804 --> 00:09:24,699
One more thing.

109
00:09:25,824 --> 00:09:29,651
You are so loyal to our school, 
but you fall for a Pathumphaisan student.

110
00:09:30,185 --> 00:09:30,890
I think…

111
00:09:31,519 --> 00:09:33,189
you must really like him.

112
00:09:35,726 --> 00:09:36,675
Yes, I do.

113
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:39,963
Then what are you waiting for? 
You should go see him.

114
00:09:40,383 --> 00:09:43,953
I’m not going to risk being beaten for free.

115
00:09:45,479 --> 00:09:46,406
Take it.

116
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,243
Thanks a lot.

117
00:09:52,025 --> 00:09:52,561
Sure.

118
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:08,142
Oh.

119
00:10:11,518 --> 00:10:12,305
Oh.

120
00:10:37,422 --> 00:10:38,390
Dear lord.

121
00:10:39,496 --> 00:10:41,889
Can you bring Oh back into my life?

122
00:10:43,301 --> 00:10:44,557
I really like him.

123
00:10:47,666 --> 00:10:49,241
Can you please tell me

124
00:10:49,905 --> 00:10:53,129
what I need to do to get him back?

125
00:11:05,957 --> 00:11:09,226
Messy, why do you have to ring a gong 
every time I pray to a higher power?

126
00:11:23,133 --> 00:11:23,961
I knew it.

127
00:11:23,961 --> 00:11:25,806
You could never beat Oh so easily.

128
00:11:25,806 --> 00:11:27,845
What do you want? Just say it.

129
00:11:28,017 --> 00:11:28,856
It’s a one-on-one fight.

130
00:11:28,856 --> 00:11:29,501
No weapons.

131
00:11:29,501 --> 00:11:30,907
The winner gets Oh’s pants.

132
00:11:31,155 --> 00:11:31,778
Start.
